pattern around `IFileSystem`, giving them a clean, testable abstraction they can extend with domain-specific behavior like logging or validation without modifying the underlying interface.","outputTokens":854,"requestId":"E3D2:2C00FF:231442E:26BEE0E:6A0536BF"},"id":"f8683eb5-4af0-4275-aa3b-de5b4905686b","timestamp":"2026-05-14T02:43:30.584Z","parentId":"d6a5d8b1-1e15-465d-a776-ff685644bc6f"}
